              <div className="font-medium mb-1">鍥剧墖绮樿创</div>
              <div className="text-[var(--editor-text)] opacity-60">Ctrl+V 鐩存帴鎻掑叆鍥剧墖</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div className="mt-8 text-xs text-[var(--editor-text)] opacity-50">
            <div className="mb-1">蹇嵎閿細Ctrl+B 鍔犵矖 | Ctrl+I 鏂滀綋 | Ctrl+S 淇濆瓨</div>
            <div>鏀寔鎷栨斁 .md 鏂囦欢鍒扮紪杈戝櫒</div>
